<h2>GreedyEPL: Greedy Expected Posterior Loss</h2>
<p>Summarises a collection of partitions into a single optimal partition. The objective function is the expected posterior loss, and the minimisation is performed through a greedy algorithm described in Rastelli, R. and Friel, N. (2016) "Optimal Bayesian estimators for latent variable cluster models" &lt;<a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1607.02325">arXiv:1607.02325</a>&gt;.</p>
